item.tootetutvustus_et:
Magic Motion Remote pult töötab nagu arvutihiir. Nutiteler ei ole nutikas, kui peate selle juhtimiseks sooritama keerulisi tegevusi. Selle puldiga saate hõlpsaimalt juhtida oma LG Smart TV telerit. Osutage, klõpsake ja juhtige, kasutades ka lohistamise ja asetamise funktsiooni. Saate hakkama ilma suure hulga nuppudeta. Ühildub kõikide LG 2011 aasta tootevaliku Smart TV teleritega.
USB vastuvõtja kuulub komplekti.
item.tootetutvustus_en:
The Magic Motion Remote Control operates like a computer mouse. A smart TV is never smart if you have to endure an overly complicated process for controlling your TV. The Magic Motion Remote Control provides the easiest control over your LG Smart TV. Just point, click, and control. With simple movements and gestures, you can drag, flick, and select your preferences, without the hassle of using multiple buttons and arrow keys. Compatible with all 2011 LG Smart TVs.
USB receiver included.

item.tootetutvustus_en:
The 5200mAH is the ideal portable battery for demanding users who require instant charge for their Smartphones or Tablets. If you are planning on being away from a mains charger for several days, the 5200mAh can store enough power for a full charge.
Users can easily charge two devices at the same time so there is no need to rely on just one device and weighing only 140g, it is hard to believe that this compact charger can give that much power!
With Maxell’s range of handy Powerbanks, you can rest easy knowing you can get that extra power boost whenever you need it. Small and lightweight enough to slip into your pocket or handbag, you’ll never be stranded without power again.

item.tootetutvustus_en:
For added convenience, all models come with Panasonic’s Wet&Dry technology so you can opt to use them in the shower or bath, eliminating the hassle of spending time cleaning up removed hairs after use.
For an even more efficient, yet gentle, result in the bath or shower, you can apply a small amount of body soap to the wet discs to create a stream of foam as the discs rotate, causing the hairs to stand up so they can be easily grasped or removed.
The foam also protects the skin from direct hit from the tweezers and prevents it from drying out after epilating, resulting in reduced skin irritation.

item.tootetutvustus_et:
• Diagnostiline fitnesskaal BS 430 Connect analüüsib keharasva, veesisalduse ja lihasmassi määra
  • Edastab mõõtmistulemused Bluetooth\'i kaudu VitaDock+ rakendusele iOS ning Android seadmetesse ning ka VitaDock® onlain keskkonnale

  • Kaalumisvõime 5-180 kg, 100 g täpsusega
VitaDock on Medisana uus kontseptsioon, mis võimaldab salvestada ja analüüsida andmeid, nagu vererõhk, veresuhkur, kehatemperatuur, kaal ja aktiivsus, kasutades samu andmeid ka teistes seadmetes. Kontseptsioon hõlmab Medisana toodetud VitaDock mõõtmisseadmeid,VitaDock Classic/VitaDock+ rakendusi ja VitaDock Online keskkonda. Üheskoos moodustavad need kasuliku andmekogumissüsteemi, mis võimaldab andmeid säilitada ja kiirelt üles leida, kui neid vaja on.
item.tootetutvustus_en:
• The diagnostic scale BS 430 Connect also analyzes the most important indicators of physical fitness such as body fat, body water and muscle mass
  • Transmits the values via Bluetooth to the VitaDock+ app for iOS and Android, and subsequently to VitaDock® online
  • Determination of the BMI value
  • Integrated calorie requirement analysis
  • 8 memory slots
  • Convenient \'step-on\' switch
  • Automatic switch-off after 8 seconds
  • Large, easy-to-read LCD display with backlight
  • High-quality electrodes
  • Toggles between kg, lb and st
  • Weighing capacity 5-180 kg, with 100 g precision
VitaDock is being revealed as a useful concept by Medisana, which allows you to save and analyze relevant data, such as blood pressure, blood sugar, body temperature, weight and activity, and to use this data on other devices. The concept includes the combination of the VitaDock measuring devices by Medisana, the VitaDock Classic/VitaDock+ App and VitaDock Online. Together, these individual components offer a useful system of data collection, storage and forwarding - so that important vital data will no longer get lost and will always be ready on hand.

VitaDock on Medisana uus kontseptsioon, mis võimaldab salvestada ja analüüsida andmeid, nagu vererõhk, veresuhkur, kehatemperatuur, kaal ja aktiivsus, kasutades samu andmeid ka teistes seadmetes. Kontseptsioon hõlmab Medisana toodetud VitaDock mõõtmisseadmeid,VitaDock Classic/VitaDock+ rakendusi ja VitaDock Online keskkonda. Üheskoos moodustavad need kasuliku andmekogumissüsteemi, mis võimaldab andmeid säilitada ja kiirelt üles leida, kui neid vaja on.
item.tootetutvustus_en:

  • Determination of the BMI value

  • Large, easy-to-read LCD display with backlight
  • High-quality electrodes
  • Toggles between kg, lb and st
  • Weighing capacity 5-180 kg, with 100 g precision
VitaDock is being revealed as a useful concept by Medisana, which allows you to save and analyze relevant data, such as blood pressure, blood sugar, body temperature, weight and activity, and to use this data on other devices. The concept includes the combination of the VitaDock measuring devices by Medisana, the VitaDock Classic/VitaDock+ App and VitaDock Online. Together, these individual components offer a useful system of data collection, storage and forwarding - so that important vital data will no longer get lost and will always be ready on hand.

• MEDISANA AIR® puhastab õhku pidevalt tolmust, õietolmust, bakteritest ja isegi lõhnadest. MEDISANA AIR® südamiku moodustab antibakteriaalne filter 3M®* ning söefilter.
  • Töötab ringleva õhu meetodil ja soodustab õhuvahetust.
  • Lülitub automaatselt päevarežiimilt öörežiimile üle.
  • Patenteeritud LED märgutuli kindlustab optimaalse filtreerimise ja osutab, kuivõrd on õhk saastunud või kas filter vajaks vahetust.
  • Vaikne ja vastupidav energiatõhus mootor võimaldab seadmel õhu täiesti puhastada umbes 60 m2 ruumis üks kord ööpäeva vältel ning 20m2 ruumis kuni 3 korda ööpäeva vältel.
item.tootetutvustus_en:
• MEDISANA AIR® purifies the air continuously and effectively from particulate matter, dust, pollen, bacteria and even smells. At the core of MEDISANA AIR® is its antibacterial particulate filter from 3M®* and additional activated carbon filter. MEDISANA AIR® works on the convection principle and promotes the exchange of air.
  • Switches automatically from day mode to a very quiet night mode.
  • The patented LED dust light ensures that the air is optimally filtered and it displays the degree of pollution or if the filter needs to be changed.
  • A quieter, more durable and energy-efficient digital motor enables the elegant air purifier to purify the air volume in an interior of about 60 m2 once every 24 hours and the air volume in rooms of approximately 20 m2 up to three times every 24 hours.

item.tootetutvustus_en:
With the Smart Baby Monitor by Withings, you can see everything you need to see and hear everything you need to hear. The alert warning feature is an innovative way to monitor your child with your iOS or Android device. You stay in total control of noise, motion, temperature and humidity. With the three-megapixel video sensor, you can enjoy impressive picture quality on your iOS or Android device. High-resolution digital video, with image stabilization and wide-angle lens, allows you to monitor your child at all times without having to move the baby monitor to a 90 angle.
Fade up a soft light in your baby\'s room, whenever you choose. Select your preferred colour, straight from your iOS or Android device and turn \'rainbow\' mode for automatic captivating colour changes.

item.tootenimi_en: Cellularline TEMPGLASBUNI45 Tempered Screen Protection Glass For 4,5\" Displays
item.tootetutvustus_et:
SECOND GLASS pole kaitsekile, vaid tõeline karastatud klaasleht, mis pakub ekraanile parimat võimalikku kaitset, säilitades ekraani kõik omadused. Pealekandmine on mullivaba. 
  • Siledaks faasitud servad
  • Ultraõhuke
  • Ei muuda ekraani tundlikkust ega eredust
  • On väga vastupidav, aga purunemisel ei murdu kildudeks vaid jääb kinnitatuks kilekihi külge, mida saab kergesti eemaldada
  • Võimaldab kasutada mudelile sobivat mistahes tüüpi telefoniümbrist
  • Klaasi tugevus 9H
item.tootetutvustus_en:
SECOND GLASS is not a protective film, but rather a real sheet of tempered glass which provides the best possible protection for your display while maintaining its original feel. Application is bubble free, and keeps your display\'s brightness and feel identical. A new dimension of protection for your smartphone\'s screen!
  • Smoothed edges
  • Ultra thin
  • It doesn\'t modify the brightness and the sensibility of the display
  • Hard and anti-bubble surface
  • Shatterproof glass: will not break up if broken, but stays attached to a film that is easy to remove
  • Usable also with phone case
  • Hardness of glass: 9H

item.tootetutvustus_et:
Freefly VR on virtuaalreaalsuse prillide komplekt, kasutamiseks koos iPhone 6/6s (sh. iPhone 6/6s Plus) ning uusimate Android nutiseadmetega. Prillid järgivad kasutaja pea liikumist 360° ja edastavad 3D visuaali telefoni ekraanilt, tekitades mulje nagu viibiksite virtuaalses maailmas. Seda nimetatakse VR ehk virtuaalreaalsus (Virtual Reality). Kui panete ette Freefly VR komplekti, satute mõne hetkega fantaasiafilmi keskele, tantsima suurejoonelisse klubisse või uudistama eksootilisi maailma paiku! Kergekaaluline seade isoleerib välisvalguse, võimaldades täielikult keskenduda virtuaalsele maailmale. Juhtmeta GLIDE kontrolleri abil on võimalik nii kolle tulistada, jalutada katakombides ringi kui ka sikutada langevarju nööre.
Prillid mahutavad kuni 150 x 95 mm suurust telefoni ja mitte paksemat kui 10 mm. Prillid ei sobi telefonide puhul, mille suurus jääb alla 135 x 50 mm.
Oluline uuendus iPhone kasutajatele:
iOS 9.2 uuendusele järgnevalt on Glide kontroller ühilduv vaid androidtelefonidega kuni järgmise uuenduseni.
 
•    Materjal – plast, pehme kunstnahk
•    Kaasas vutlar
•    120° vaateväli
•    Ühilduv enamiku nutitelefonidega
•    Glide VR kontroller kaasas
•    Kergekaaluline
•    Mõõtmed 140x245x190
•    Kaal 786 g
item.tootetutvustus_en:
The Freefly VR is a smartphone adapter that allows virtual reality content to be experienced with the smartphone that most people already carry in their pockets. Within seconds of wearing the Freefly VR, you can be sitting in a fantasy theater, dancing through the clubs or touring exotic locations! 

Music videos, movies and games that can be downloaded from Google Play and the App Store are all pushing forward into virtual reality, offering 3D 360 degree worlds to explore. The lightweight device blocks external light allowing you to truly lose yourself in another world.

The Freefly VR has quickly become well-known as the number one mobile-powered VR headset for those looking for great immersion, great design and ease of use. Every part of the device has been designed with user comfort, simplicity and immersion in mind.
The faux-leather adds style and comfort and the wing mechanism means more customers can use the Freefly VR than any other headset, independant of whether they use Apple or Android phones. The large lenses offer a market-leading 120 degree field-of-view and the unique GLIDE VR controller adds wireless interactive support to a growing range of VR titles.

The Freefly VR is adjustable for screen sizes of 4.7 to 6.1 inches allowing many phones to be used, including the latest iPhone 6 (and 6 Plus), Samsung S3, S4, S5 and S6, Samsung Note 3&4 and many more. Other features of the Freefly VR include:
  • Wide 42 mm lenses for maximum field of immersion;
  • Unique and best closing mechanism for various phone sizes (4.7 – 6.1”);
  • Automatic phone thickness adjuster (6 – 13mm);
  • Lightweight design;
  • 1-click quick open system;
  • Ergonomic design;
  • Anti-fog lens coating;
  • Extra comfort with soft faux-leather;
  • Comes with a carry-on box and lens cloth;
  • Free included wireless GLIDE VR Bluetooth controller
